# Scenario: Field aliasing
# Why: Tests that the GraphQL alias syntax (alias: name) correctly maps to RQL aliases.
query 'CALL graphql::explain("query { txs: transactions { tx_hash: hash } }")'
---
> +-------+--------+-----------------------+
> |  idx  |  kind  |        detail         |
> +-------+--------+-----------------------+
> |   0   |  From  |  transactions as txs  |
> |   1   |  Map   |    hash as tx_hash    |
> +-------+--------+-----------------------+
>
